# Normalize all text to LF on checkout, on every platform (Windows included).
# luaur has line-ending-sensitive tests — the lexer's newline handling and the
# byte-exact bytecode differential over `.luau` fixtures both compare exact
# bytes — so a CRLF checkout on Windows would spuriously fail them. Forcing LF
# keeps the suite identical across Linux / macOS / Windows.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets — never touch.
*.png   binary
*.jpg   binary
*.jpeg  binary
*.gif   binary
*.ico   binary
*.woff  binary
*.woff2 binary
*.wasm  binary
